#: selfdrive/ui/mici/layouts/settings/firehose.py

msgid "Firehose Mode"
msgstr "Firehose 模式"

msgid "sunnypilot learns to drive by watching humans, like you, drive.\n\nFirehose Mode allows you to maximize your training data uploads to improve openpilot's driving models. More data means bigger models, which means better Experimental Mode."
msgstr "sunnypilot 通过观察人类驾驶来学习自动驾驶。\n\nFirehose 模式可最大化你的训练数据上传量，用于提升 openpilot 驾驶模型。数据越多，模型越强，辅助驾驶效果也越好。"

msgid "For maximum effectiveness, bring your device inside and connect to a good USB-C adapter and Wi-Fi weekly.\n\nFirehose Mode can also work while you're driving if connected to a hotspot or unlimited SIM card."
msgstr "为达到最佳效果，请每周将设备带回室内，连接优质 USB‑C 充电器和 Wi‑Fi。\n\n如果连接热点或无限流量 SIM 卡，Firehose 模式也可在行驶中工作。"

msgid "Frequently Asked Questions"
msgstr "常见问题"

msgid "Does it matter how or where I drive?"
msgstr "驾驶方式或地点有影响吗？" 

msgid "Do all of my segments get pulled in Firehose Mode?"
msgstr "Firehose 模式会上传我所有的驾驶片段吗？"


msgid "What's a good USB-C adapter?"
msgstr "什么样的 USB‑C 充电器比较好？"

msgid "Does it matter which software I run?"
msgstr "我使用的系统版本有影响吗？"

msgid "ACTIVE"
msgstr "已激活"

msgid "INACTIVE: connect to an unmetered network"
msgstr "未激活:请连接非计量网络（Wi‑Fi/无限流量）"

msgid "{} segment of your driving is in the training dataset so far."
msgstr "目前已有 {} 段你的驾驶数据加入训练集。"

