msgstr "开启后，行驶界面不显示时速表。"

msgid "Display Turn Signals"
msgstr "显示转向灯"

msgid "When enabled, visual turn indicators are drawn on the HUD."
msgstr "开启后，HUD 上显示转向指示灯。"

msgid "Real-time Acceleration Bar"
msgstr "实时加减速条"

msgid "Show an indicator on the left side of the screen to display real-time vehicle acceleration and deceleration. This displays what the car is currently doing, not what the planner is requesting."
msgstr "屏幕左侧显示车辆实时加减速状态，显示车辆实际动作而非规划值。"

msgid "Display Metrics Below Chevron"
msgstr "在引导箭头下方显示指标"

