msgid "Auto Lane Change by Blinker"
msgstr "转向灯自动变道"

msgid "Set a timer to delay the auto lane change operation when the blinker is used. No nudge on the steering wheel is required to auto lane change if a timer is set. Default is Nudge.<br>Please use caution when using this feature. Only use the blinker when traffic and road conditions permit."
msgstr "设置使用转向灯自动变道的延迟时间。设置时间后无需轻拨方向盘即可自动变道。默认需要轻拨方向盘。<br>使用此功能时请务必谨慎，仅在路况允许时使用转向灯。"

msgid "Nudge"
msgstr "轻拨方向盘"
msgid "Nudgeless"
msgstr "无需轻拨"

msgid "Auto Lane Change: Delay with Blind Spot"
msgstr "自动变道:盲区检测延迟"

msgid "Toggle to enable a delay timer for seamless lane changes when blind spot monitoring (BSM) detects a obstructing vehicle, ensuring safe maneuvering."
msgstr "开启后，若盲区监测（BSM）检测到车辆，会自动延迟变道，确保变道安全。"

